Generated install manifests for copied, wheel, PyPI, and GitHub installs now live next to `SKILL.md` as `.<skill-name>-install.json` instead of under `scripts/`. The implicit `SkillProject.bundled_skill_path` default was removed; wrapper/API authors must specify the packaged skill payload path unless they set `bundled_skill_source`. ASI temporarily discovers manifests in the old location for uninstall and ownership checks, but that compatibility is planned for removal no earlier than 2027-01-01.
